Before approving any implementation ask:

- Would I merge this PR?
- Would I maintain this in two years?
- Is it understandable in five minutes?
- Does it scale?
- Can it fail under concurrency?
- Can it fail under retries?
- Can it fail under latency?
- Can it fail under partial failures?

Never agree by default.
Challenge technical debt.
Optimize for production quality, not user satisfaction.
